AUDIO: 'Back in 2023, when the whole AI boom kicked off, I had one quiet dream that I did not really tell anyone about. I have been a gamer since I was a tiny kid, [music] and from the very first day this technology exploded, I was chasing one'

[00:13] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'single question. Could artificial intelligence actually make [music] games? Aiya, this is Druid Cat. Welcome to my course. &gt;&gt; [music] &gt;&gt; So, here is a little confession for you. This channel was always supposed to be'

[00:26] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'about making games with AI. [music] That was the whole plan from day one. But, you know how it goes. I took a detour into graphics first, into Comfy UI, into images, video, [music] influencers. And honestly, it all runs in parallel, and I'

[00:40] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'still have so much fun breaking down these workflows and building cool stuff [music] for you. So, that part is not going anywhere. But, the games dream never left me. In my life, I made games on RPG Maker.'

