VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'about it, you can go and play it right now. The link is sitting right there in the description. So, what is it, exactly? It is a simple browser game that takes the idea of the classic Blobby Volley, the one the millennials'

[02:57] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'among you will absolutely remember, and gives it a fresh coat of paint, plus a set of extra superpowers, because a plain volley was just not chaotic enough for me. Pull one off at the right moment, and'

